394
00:49:10,637 --> 00:49:18,264
I think it aligns with what they, you know, their mission and what they do.

395
00:49:20,907 --> 00:49:26,632
I don't think the ZBA or the Affordable Housing Trust Fund boards make as much sense.

396
00:49:41,641 --> 00:49:44,464
Great, yeah, I think that makes a lot of sense as the next step.

